q6 module¶

q6.processData(input_path, output_path)¶

Groups data based on the age field in the json file and store the output again as a .json file. Output json file will contain an array of 2 json objects. Only those records are considered whose isActive field is true .

Parameters

  • input_path (str) – input json file path

  • output_path (str) – output json file path

q6.produceresult(data, age_grp)¶

Process the data given and create a desired dict result

Parameters

  • data (dict) – input json content

  • age_grp (str) – age_grp value which is needed to process the data

Returns

processed dict object

Return type

dict
